<br>
1. The original post isnt that well thought out.  When paladins were looking for a role on big raids, we found a niche that did not exist, the ae heal.  <br>
<br>
In suggesting this we enabled verant to give us a role that didnt cut into anyone else's role.  <br>
<br>
Verant rightly ignored our request for defensive as it would cut into the warrior role too much.<br>
<br>
I think druids should be upgraded, but they need to put their heads together and come up with something creative and not piggy back on another class's role.<br>
<br>
2. The respsonses are 99% &quot;/I agree by Treehugger lvl 35 druid.&quot;<br>
<br>
There needs to be more debate and refining of ideas within the community. Especially since there is nothing new or creative in this petition other than &quot;gimme some of what other classes do.&quot;<br>
<br>
I truely hope druids get upgraded so that they have a bigger role in raids.  I just think this petition doesnt do much to help their cause.<br>
<br>
